209 §41-27A-4
210 (a)(1) An Advisory Committee is established to ensure
211 that state and local interests are considered by the GIS
212 Executive Council.
213 (2) The Advisory Committee shall have all of the
214 following purposes:
215 a. Foster communication and cooperation among state,
